    interviewQuestions: ['How do containers differ from virtual machines in terms of architecture?', 'Explain how Docker image layering works and why it matters for efficiency.', 'What is the difference between Docker Compose and Kubernetes?', 'How does Docker handle networking between containers?', 'What are best practices for writing efficient Dockerfiles?'],
